// src/Characters.js import React from 'react'; import './Characters.css'; const Characters = () => { return (

Meet the Friends Characters

Character Name: Ross Geller

Description: A paleontologist with a knack for sarcasm and awkward situations. Known for his "We were on a break!" moment.

Character Name: Rachel Green

Description: A fashion enthusiast with a journey from waitress to a high-profile fashion career. Always stylish and confident.

Character Name: Monica Geller

Description: The competitive and organized chef who loves hosting and keeping things tidy. Sister to Ross.

Character Name: Chandler Bing

Description: The sarcastic and witty office worker who is the king of one-liners. Best friends with Joey.

Character Name: Phoebe Buffay

Description: The quirky and lovable musician with a unique worldview. Known for her hit song "Smelly Cat."

Character Name: Joey Tribbiani

Description: The aspiring actor with a love for food and a catchphrase: "How you doin'?" Always the life of the party.

); }; export default Characters;
